==Finnish==
===Etymology===
Derived from ''[[nähdä]]''
===Interjection===
'''nääs'''

#(''slang'') [[see]] ''(singular imperative)''.
#:*''Se on nääs sillä lailla.'' See, that’s the way it is.
#(:The plural imperative is ''[[nähkääs]]''.)

Used especially in the Tampere and Etelä-Pirkanmaa dialect.

